    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="P91-23">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>A poor torn heart, a tattered heart,</l>
                    <l>That sat it down to rest,</l>
                    <l>Nor noticed that the ebbing day</l>
                    <l>Flowed silver to the west,</l>
                    <l>Nor noticed night did soft descend</l>
                    <l>Nor constellation burn,</l>
                    <l>Intent upon the vision</l>
                    <l>Of latitudes unknown.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The angels, happening that way,</l>
                    <l>This dusty heart espied;</l>
                    <l>Tenderly took it up from toil</l>
                    <l>And carried it to God.</l>
                    <l>There,  sandals for the barefoot;</l>
                    <l>There,  gathered from the gales,</l>
                    <l>Do the blue havens by the hand</l>
                    <l>Lead the wandering sails.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
